  "detailed_description": "<strong>Urban Escape offers a fast paced parkour game with some action elements in a toon world.</strong><br><br>Do whatever it takes to progress upwards and onwards. Run on the walls, dash forward, slow the time down, use grapple and jetpack and even a jet!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/27e06d30b98130ce6b6d381da39070a0.poster.avif?t=1740494833\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/27e06d30b98130ce6b6d381da39070a0.webm?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/27e06d30b98130ce6b6d381da39070a0.mp4?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>This journey will take you through various locations like the city and even space!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/86744a91016ebb55b59a0c412f55e3a6.poster.avif?t=1740494833\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/86744a91016ebb55b59a0c412f55e3a6.webm?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/86744a91016ebb55b59a0c412f55e3a6.mp4?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Be aware of possible dangers, escape from them and defend yourself with your bomb. And never stop trying until you reach your destination.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/0e289d8644beb312ce793369f234dbd5.poster.avif?t=1740494833\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/0e289d8644beb312ce793369f234dbd5.webm?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/0e289d8644beb312ce793369f234dbd5.mp4?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Also try the special modes; speedrun mode or free roam mode.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Urban Escape offers a fast paced parkour game with some action elements in a toon world.</strong><br><br>Do whatever it takes to progress upwards and onwards. Run on the walls, dash forward, slow the time down, use grapple and jetpack and even a jet!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/27e06d30b98130ce6b6d381da39070a0.poster.avif?t=1740494833\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/27e06d30b98130ce6b6d381da39070a0.webm?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/27e06d30b98130ce6b6d381da39070a0.mp4?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>This journey will take you through various locations like the city and even space!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/86744a91016ebb55b59a0c412f55e3a6.poster.avif?t=1740494833\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/86744a91016ebb55b59a0c412f55e3a6.webm?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/86744a91016ebb55b59a0c412f55e3a6.mp4?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Be aware of possible dangers, escape from them and defend yourself with your bomb. And never stop trying until you reach your destination.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/0e289d8644beb312ce793369f234dbd5.poster.avif?t=1740494833\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/0e289d8644beb312ce793369f234dbd5.webm?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700380/extras/0e289d8644beb312ce793369f234dbd5.mp4?t=1740494833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Also try the special modes; speedrun mode or free roam mode.",
